{"tid":759801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友同我講要去船P","createTime":"2018-07-29T03:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T07:55:59.000Z","uid":73596,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f556f0063ed7a2eee639318448f69e3a63ddb11c","tid":759801,"uid":73596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"交代下先，同女朋友係大學同學，當年曖昧咗好耐最後都冇一齊到(其實係我衰，唔敢開口同埋後尾覺得照顧佢好攰)<br />\n<br />\n之後隔咗幾年再聯絡番，中間大家都有拍過拖。到近期我地終於一齊咗，不過佢話其實仲未覺得我係男朋友，宜家感覺同朋友拍拖好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我講既情話，支持佢鼓勵佢既說話，佢都冇咩回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排傾傾下偈，佢同我講約咗幾個女仔fd一齊去船P... 其實好心up，自問一直對佢好好，今日我聽到佢之後要去船P既消息，我仲諗住煲湯去俾佢飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以屌醒我?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15345967f3d94bbc0d506bf52097d02c4f0b61e5","tid":759801,"uid":73462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"一齊去no problem"},{"pid":"038e1356cb9806fa429343cabc9cb7ed0b6a9077","tid":759801,"uid":146699,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"兵only"},{"pid":"5f5d12092c128ec71b10e63645d153232132bd96","tid":759801,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾亂棍毆死？"},{"pid":"ec9d4253a9864fe76fc9aaf9cff716ad1370b54d","tid":759801,"uid":113807,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你自己FF做左佢BF?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc19fa0c5b99f76d0e5eac6c31cf9a3e5d1afb72","tid":759801,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d96ca94446e49c381d73f5d95b348ddf66829b0","tid":759801,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"